<%- contentFor('body') %>
<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <div class="mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">検証用ウェブ アプリ</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-lg">シンプルで使いやすい機能を提供する実験的なウェブアプリケーション</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-6 mb-12">
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">機能一覧</h2>
            <div class="grid gap-4">
                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4 p-4 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900 flex items-center justify-center">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">データベース接続確認</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-1">PostgreSQLデータベースとの接続状態を監視</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4 p-4 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900 flex items-center justify-center">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">CRUD操作の実装</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-1">基本的なデータ操作機能を提供</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4 p-4 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900 flex items-center justify-center">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">AWS S3への画像アップロード</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-1">クラウドストレージを活用した画像管理</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4 p-4 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900 flex items-center justify-center">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">PostgreSQLとPrisma</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-1">モダンなORMを使用したデータベース操作</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4 p-4 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
