                            <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white group-hover:text-blue-600 dark:group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">システム状態</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-1">システムの健全性を確認できます</p>
                        </div>
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 group-hover:text-blue-600 dark:group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                </a>

                <a href="/microposts" class="block p-4 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow group">
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white group-hover:text-blue-600 dark:group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">投稿一覧</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-1">画像付きの投稿を作成・閲覧できます</p>
